# She Goes Outside 🌿

**Adventures for women who love exploring, good food, fresh air, and great company.**

A static website for *She Goes Outside*, founded by JoAnne Yorkston — an outdoor adventure community for women in the Pacific Northwest and beyond.

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
she-goes-outside/
├── index.html          # Home page
├── about.html          # About JoAnne & the brand story
├── events.html         # Upcoming events (filterable)
├── calendar.html       # Monthly event calendar
├── blog.html           # Adventure blog / articles
├── faq.html            # Frequently asked questions
├── contact.html        # Contact form + social links
├── css/
│   ├── styles.css      # All shared styles & components
│   └── illustrations.css  # Notes on SVG placeholder system
├── js/
│   └── main.js         # Nav, FAQ accordion, filter, calendar
└── images/             # Drop your real photos here
```

---

